drop table "CON_StepRecord" cascade constraints;

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: "CON_StepRecord" */
/*==============================================================*/
create table "CON_StepRecord"
(
"StepID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"ContractID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"CompanyID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"CompanyCode" VARCHAR2(20) not null,
"EntityID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"EntityCode" VARCHAR2(20) not null,
"MallID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"MallCode" VARCHAR2(20) not null,
"BuildingID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"BuildingCode" VARCHAR2(20) not null,
"Step" INTEGER not null,
"RecordTime" TIMESTAMP not null,
"RecordBy" NUMBER(32) not null,
constraint PK_CON_STEPRECORD primary key ("StepID")
);

comment on column "CON_StepRecord"."Step" is
'

10:合同信息(招商)
20:合同条款(招商)
30:合同优惠(招商)
40:合同打印及其他条款(招商)

80:合同信息(财务复核)
90:合同优惠(财务完成优惠调整并确定)';
